== Events == * {{ill|Bunmei (Japan)|ja|文明|qq=|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Bunmei (Japan)|qq=}} 14th year ({{ill|Julian calendar|1=Julian calendar|2=ja|3=ユリウス暦|4=zh|5=儒略曆|6=ru|7=Юлианский_календарь|8=de|9=Julianischer_Kalender|10=es|11=Calendario juliano|ja|ユリウス暦|1=Julian calendar|2=ja|3=ユリウス暦|4=zh|5=儒略曆|6=ru|7=Юлианский_календарь|8=de|9=Julianischer_Kalender|10=es|11=Calendario juliano|qq=|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Julian calendar|13=User:Immanuelle/Julian calendar|qq=}} {{ill|1483|ja|1483|qq=|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/1483|qq=}} {{ill|January 6|ja|1月6日|qq=|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/January 6|qq=}} ) – The Muromachi shogunate and {{ill|Furukawa|ja|古河公方|qq=|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Furukawa|qq=}} ’s {{ill|Ashikaga Narushi|ja|足利成氏|qq=|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Ashikaga Narushi|qq=}} reached an accord that ended the internal strife (the {{ill|Kyōtoku no Ran|ja|享徳の乱|qq=|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Kyōtoku no Ran|qq=}} ) in the Kantō region which had persisted since 1455. * {{ill|Tenmon (era)|ja|天文|qq=|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Tenmon (era)|qq=}} 18th year ({{ill|Julian calendar|1=Julian calendar|2=ja|3=ユリウス暦|4=zh|5=儒略曆|6=ru|7=Юлианский_календарь|8=de|9=Julianischer_Kalender|10=es|11=Calendario juliano|ja|ユリウス暦|1=Julian calendar|2=ja|3=ユリウス暦|4=zh|5=儒略曆|6=ru|7=Юлианский_календарь|8=de|9=Julianischer_Kalender|10=es|11=Calendario juliano|qq=|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Julian calendar|13=User:Immanuelle/Julian calendar|qq=}} {{ill|1549|ja|1549|qq=|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/1549|qq=}} {{ill|December 15|ja|12月15日|qq=|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/December 15|qq=}} ) – The Matsudaira domain of Mikawa fell under the control of {{ill|Imagawa Yoshimoto|ja|今川義元|qq=|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Imagawa Yoshimoto|qq=}} , and Takechiyo (later known as {{ill|Tokugawa Ieyasu|ja|徳川家康|qq=|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Tokugawa Ieyasu|qq=}} ) was sent as a hostage to Sunpu. * {{ill|Bunsei|ja|文政|qq=|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Bunsei|qq=}} 10th year ({{ill|Gregorian calendar|1=Gregorian calendar|2=ja|3=グレゴリオ暦|4=fr|5=Calendrier grégorien|6=de|7=Gregorianischer Kalender|8=tl|9=Kalendaryong Gregoryano|10=ru|11=Григорианский календарь|ja|グレゴリオ暦|qq=|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Gregorian calendar|13=User:Immanuelle/Gregorian calendar|qq=}} {{ill|1828|ja|1828|qq=|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/1828|qq=}} {{ill|January 13|ja|1月13日|qq=|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/January 13|qq=}} ) – {{ill|Tokugawa Ienari|ja|徳川家斉|qq=|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Tokugawa Ienari|qq=}} built a gate ({{ill|Omamiden|ja|御守殿門|qq=|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Omamiden|qq=}} , now the red gate of the University of Tokyo’s Hongo campus) on the estate of the Maeda clan in Kaga. * {{ill|Ansei|ja|安政|qq=|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Ansei|qq=}} 1st year ({{ill|Gregorian calendar|1=Gregorian calendar|2=ja|3=グレゴリオ暦|4=fr|5=Calendrier grégorien|6=de|7=Gregorianischer Kalender|8=tl|9=Kalendaryong Gregoryano|10=ru|11=Григорианский календарь|ja|グレゴリオ暦|qq=|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Gregorian calendar|13=User:Immanuelle/Gregorian calendar|qq=}} {{ill|1855|ja|1855|qq=|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/1855|qq=}} {{ill|January 15|ja|1月15日|qq=|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/January 15|qq=}} ) – The era name was changed from {{ill|Kaien|ja|嘉永|qq=|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Kaien|qq=}} to {{ill|Ansei|ja|安政|qq=|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Ansei|qq=}} . * {{ill|Meiji|ja|明治|1=Meiji era|qq=|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Meiji|13=User:Immanuelle/Meiji era|qq=}} 5th year ({{ill|Gregorian calendar|1=Gregorian calendar|2=ja|3=グレゴリオ暦|4=fr|5=Calendrier grégorien|6=de|7=Gregorianischer Kalender|8=tl|9=Kalendaryong Gregoryano|10=ru|11=Григорианский календарь|ja|グレゴリオ暦|qq=|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Gregorian calendar|13=User:Immanuelle/Gregorian calendar|qq=}} {{ill|1872|ja|1872|qq=|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/1872|qq=}} {{ill|December 27|ja|12月27日|qq=|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/December 27|qq=}} ) – A notice was issued by the Daijōkan for non-payment of salaries for December.
== Births == * {{ill|Kōji (Japan)|ja|Kōji|qq=|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Kōji (Japan)|qq=}} 1st year ({{ill|Julian calendar|1=Julian calendar|2=ja|3=ユリウス暦|4=zh|5=儒略曆|6=ru|7=Юлианский_календарь|8=de|9=Julianischer_Kalender|10=es|11=Calendario juliano|ja|ユリウス暦|1=Julian calendar|2=ja|3=ユリウス暦|4=zh|5=儒略曆|6=ru|7=Юлианский_календарь|8=de|9=Julianischer_Kalender|10=es|11=Calendario juliano|qq=|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Julian calendar|13=User:Immanuelle/Julian calendar|qq=}} {{ill|1556|ja|1556|qq=|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/1556|qq=}} {{ill|January 8|ja|1月8日|qq=|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/January 8|qq=}} ) – {{ill|Uesugi Kagekatsu|ja|上杉景勝|qq=|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Uesugi Kagekatsu|qq=}} , a daimyō († {{ill|1623|ja|1623|qq=|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/1623|qq=}} ).
== Deaths == * {{ill|Ōchō|ja|応長|qq=|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Ōchō|qq=}} 1st year ({{ill|Julian calendar|1=Julian calendar|2=ja|3=ユリウス暦|4=zh|5=儒略曆|6=ru|7=Юлианский_календарь|8=de|9=Julianischer_Kalender|10=es|11=Calendario juliano|ja|ユリウス暦|1=Julian calendar|2=ja|3=ユリウス暦|4=zh|5=儒略曆|6=ru|7=Юлианский_календарь|8=de|9=Julianischer_Kalender|10=es|11=Calendario juliano|qq=|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Julian calendar|13=User:Immanuelle/Julian calendar|qq=}} {{ill|1311|ja|1311|qq=|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/1311|qq=}} {{ill|November 3|ja|11月3日|qq=|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/November 3|qq=}} ) – {{ill|Hojo Ujitoki|ja|北条師時|qq=|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Hojo Ujitoki|qq=}} , the 10th shikken of the Kamakura shogunate (* {{ill|1275|ja|1275|qq=|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/1275|qq=}} ). * {{ill|An'ei|ja|安永|qq=|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/An'ei|qq=}} 2nd year ({{ill|Gregorian calendar|1=Gregorian calendar|2=ja|3=グレゴリオ暦|4=fr|5=Calendrier grégorien|6=de|7=Gregorianischer Kalender|8=tl|9=Kalendaryong Gregoryano|10=ru|11=Григорианский календарь|ja|グレゴリオ暦|qq=|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Gregorian calendar|13=User:Immanuelle/Gregorian calendar|qq=}} {{ill|1773|ja|1773|qq=|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/1773|qq=}} {{ill|October 22|ja|10月22日|qq=|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/October 22|qq=}} ) – {{ill|Tanuma Iamasa|ja|田沼意明|qq=|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Tanuma Iamasa|qq=}} , the first lord of the Mutsu Shimomura domain (* {{ill|1796|ja|1796|qq=|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/1796|qq=}} ). * {{ill|Bunsei|ja|文政|qq=|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Bunsei|qq=}} 12th year ({{ill|Gregorian calendar|1=Gregorian calendar|2=ja|3=グレゴリオ暦|4=fr|5=Calendrier grégorien|6=de|7=Gregorianischer Kalender|8=tl|9=Kalendaryong Gregoryano|10=ru|11=Григорианский календарь|ja|グレゴリオ暦|qq=|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Gregorian calendar|13=User:Immanuelle/Gregorian calendar|qq=}} {{ill|1829|ja|1829|qq=|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/1829|qq=}} {{ill|December 22|ja|12月22日|qq=|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/December 22|qq=}} ) – The 4th generation leader of {{ill|Tsuruyanin|ja|鶴屋南北|qq=|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Tsuruyanin|qq=}} , a kabuki dramatist (* {{ill|1755|ja|1755|qq=|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/1755|qq=}} ).
