== Births == * {{ill|Kōji (Japan)|1=Kōji (Muromachi period)|2=ja|3=弘治 (日本)|lt=Kōji|4=ru|5=Кодзи (Муромати)|ja|Kōji|qq=|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Kōji (Japan)|1=Kōji (Muromachi period)|2=ja|3=弘治 (日本)|lt=Kōji|4=ru|5=Кодзи (Муромати)|qq=}} 1st year ([[:en:Julian calendar|Julian calendar]] {{ill|1556|ja|1556|qq=|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/1556|qq=}} [[:en:January 8|January 8]] ) – [[:en:Uesugi Kagekatsu|Uesugi Kagekatsu]] , a daimyō († {{ill|1623|ja|1623|qq=|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/1623|qq=}} ).
== Deaths == * [[:en:Ōchō|Ōchō]] 1st year ([[:en:Julian calendar|Julian calendar]] {{ill|1311|ja|1311|qq=|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/1311|qq=}} [[:en:November 3|November 3]] ) – [[:en:Hōjō Morotoki|Hojo Ujitoki]] , the 10th shikken of the Kamakura shogunate (* {{ill|1275|ja|1275|qq=|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/1275|qq=}} ). * {{ill|An'ei|ja|安永|qq=|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/An'ei|qq=}} 2nd year ([[:en:Gregorian calendar|Gregorian calendar]] {{ill|1773|ja|1773|qq=|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/1773|qq=}} [[:en:October 22|October 22]] ) – {{ill|Tanuma Iamasa|ja|田沼意明|qq=|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Tanuma Iamasa|qq=}} , the first lord of the Mutsu Shimomura domain (* {{ill|1796|ja|1796|qq=|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/1796|qq=}} ). * [[:en:Bunsei|Bunsei]] 12th year ([[:en:Gregorian calendar|Gregorian calendar]] {{ill|1829|ja|1829|qq=|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/1829|qq=}} [[:en:December 22|December 22]] ) – The 4th generation leader of {{ill|Tsuruyanin|ja|鶴屋南北|qq=|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Tsuruyanin|qq=}} , a kabuki dramatist (* {{ill|1755|ja|1755|qq=|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/1755|qq=}} ).
