== Births == * [[:en:Kōji (Muromachi period)|Kōji]] 1st year ([[:en:Julian calendar|Julian calendar]] [[:en:1556|1556]] [[:en:January 8|January 8]] ) – [[:en:Uesugi Kagekatsu|Uesugi Kagekatsu]] , a daimyō († [[:en:1623|1623]] ).
== Deaths == * [[:en:Ōchō|Ōchō]] 1st year ([[:en:Julian calendar|Julian calendar]] [[:en:1311|1311]] [[:en:November 3|November 3]] ) – [[:en:Hōjō Morotoki|Hojo Ujitoki]] , the 10th shikken of the Kamakura shogunate (* [[:en:1275|1275]] ). * {{ill|An'ei|ja|安永|qq=|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/An'ei|qq=|ja_comment=jawiki redirects to 安永 (元号)}} 2nd year ([[:en:Gregorian calendar|Gregorian calendar]] [[:en:1773|1773]] [[:en:October 22|October 22]] ) – {{ill|Tanuma Iamasa|ja|田沼意明|qq=|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Tanuma Iamasa|qq=}} , the first lord of the Mutsu Shimomura domain (* [[:en:1796|1796]] ). * [[:en:Bunsei|Bunsei]] 12th year ([[:en:Gregorian calendar|Gregorian calendar]] {{ill|1829|ja|1829|qq=|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/1829|qq=|ja_comment=jawiki link invalid}} [[:en:December 22|December 22]] ) – The 4th generation leader of {{ill|Tsuruyanin|ja|鶴屋南北|qq=|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Tsuruyanin|qq=}} , a kabuki dramatist (* [[:en:1755|1755]] ).
